        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-932534693" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-932534693" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="932534693">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/angelmagazine/">漆黑天使复活</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2015-06-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">看过的大部分旅行书都有一种通病，矫情，过多的个人情感流露，相比之下《不去会死》那种平铺直述来的更真实</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="927360091">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-927360091" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-927360091" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="927360091">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/pepper7mint/">柯柯柯尼</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-05-31</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">“真正使我们迷失的是我们的无明，贪欲，不安全感，想走捷径。”深以为然。在地铁上读完了傅真，很自然地被书中那种理智和疯狂吸引。旅行对她和铭基的意义早已不是出去而是回来，在行走和感受中不断试探，最终寻找到通向内心的道路。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="889213189">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-889213189" class="vote-count">14</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-889213189" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="889213189">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/MichelleHong/">Super小麦</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-02-01</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">依然并非是游记。缅甸那段尤其好~这样一对佳人，还是真正的令人心服口服，与某些网站推的，或者有些出书的基本不在一个等级。如此美妙的探险，只是看看游记也能觉得欣慰。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="886107868">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
